<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Account Successfully Deleted - BIGHIL</title>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }
        
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
        }
        
        .email-container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        }
        
        .header {
            background-color: #ffffff;
            padding: 30px 20px;
            text-align: center;
            border-bottom: 2px solid #198754;
        }
        
        .logo {
            max-width: 150px;
            height: auto;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }
        
        .app-name {
            font-size: 28px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #198754;
            margin: 0;
        }
        
        .content {
            background-color: #198754;
            color: #ffffff;
            padding: 40px 30px;
        }
        
        .content h1 {
            font-size: 24px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        
        .content p {
            font-size: 16px;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        
        .info-box {
            background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            margin: 25px 0;
            border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
        }
        
        .info-box h3 {
            font-size: 18px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            color: #ffffff;
        }
        
        .info-box ul {
            list-style: none;
            padding-left: 0;
        }
        
        .info-box li {
            margin-bottom: 8px;
            padding-left: 15px;
            position: relative;
        }
        
        .info-box li:before {
            content: "âœ“";
            position: absolute;
            left: 0;
            color: #ffffff;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        
        .cta-section {
            text-align: center;
            margin: 30px 0;
        }
        
        .btn {
            display: inline-block;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            color: #198754;
            padding: 12px 30px;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 6px;
            font-weight: bold;
            font-size: 16px;
            margin: 10px;
            transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
        }
        
        .btn:hover {
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
        }
        
        .footer {
            background-color: #ffffff;
            padding: 30px 20px;
            text-align: center;
            border-top: 2px solid #198754;
        }
        
        .footer p {
            color: #666;
            font-size: 14px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        
        .support-info {
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        
        .support-email {
            color: #198754;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        
        .support-email:hover {
            text-decoration: underline;
        }
        
        /* Mobile Responsive */
        @media only screen and (max-width: 600px) {
            .email-container {
                width: 100% !important;
                margin: 0;
            }
            
            .header {
                padding: 20px 15px;
            }
            
        
            
            .content {
                padding: 30px 20px;
            }
            
            .content h1 {
                font-size: 20px;
            }
            
            .content p {
                font-size: 14px;
            }
            
            .info-box {
                padding: 15px;
                margin: 20px 0;
            }
            
            .info-box h3 {
                font-size: 16px;
            }
            
            .btn {
                display: block;
                margin: 15px 0;
                padding: 15px 20px;
                font-size: 14px;
            }
            
            .footer {
                padding: 20px 15px;
            }
            
            .footer p {
                font-size: 12px;
            }
        }
        
        @media only screen and (max-width: 480px) {
            .content {
                padding: 25px 15px;
            }
            
            .info-box {
                padding: 12px;
            }
            
            .logo {
                max-width: 120px;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="email-container">
        <!-- Header Section -->
        <div class="header">
            <% if (logoPath) { %>
                <img src="<%= logoPath %>" alt="BIGHIL Logo" class="logo">
            <% } %>
          
        </div>
        
        <!-- Main Content -->
        <div class="content">
            <h1>Account Successfully Deleted</h1>
            
            <p>We're sorry to see you go! Your BIGHIL account has been successfully deleted as requested.</p>
            
            <div class="info-box">
                <h3>What happens next:</h3>
                <ul>
                    <li>All your data has been permanently removed</li>
                    <li>Your account access has been revoked</li>
                    <li>All associated data and preferences have been deleted</li>
                    <li>You will no longer receive communications from us</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            
            <p>If you change your mind, you're always welcome to create a new account with us.</p>
            
            <div class="cta-section">
                <% if (signUpLink) { %>
                    <a href="<%= signUpLink %>" class="btn">Create New Account</a>
                <% } %>
            </div>
            
            <p>Thank you for being part of the BIGHIL community. We wish you all the best!</p>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Footer Section -->
        <div class="footer">
            <div class="support-info">
                <p>Need help or have questions?</p>
                <% if (supportEmail) { %>
                    <a href="mailto:<%= supportEmail %>" class="support-email"><%= supportEmail %></a>
                <% } %>
            </div>
            
            <p>This is an automated message. Please do not reply to this email.</p>
            <p>&copy; <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> BIGHIL. All rights reserved.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>